the ChibiRyS Tote Bag, illustrated by Lien-sensei,

841
01:02:22,897 --> 01:02:27,897
the Race QueenRyS Keychain, which is a really cute Race Queen plushie keychain,

842
01:02:27,897 --> 01:02:30,897
and the YabaiRyS Pouch.

843
01:02:30,897 --> 01:02:37,397
For full set bonuses, the limited edition includes a postcard with a handwritten message and a foil-stamped autograph.

844
01:02:37,397 --> 01:02:42,397
The standard version includes a postcard with both a foil-stamped message and autograph.

845
01:02:42,397 --> 01:02:48,397
And sales will start at 1:15 PM, which is like real soon if not maybe even now.

846
01:02:48,397 --> 01:02:55,897
フルセットを買っていただいた方には、数量限定版は直筆メッセージ＆箔押し複製サイン入りポストカードが付いてきます。
For those who purchase the full set, the limited edition includes a postcard with a handwritten message and a foil-stamped copy of my autograph.

847
01:02:55,897 --> 01:03:01,397
通常バージョンは、箔押し複製サイン＆メッセージ入りポストカードになります。
The standard version will include a postcard with a foil-stamped copy of my autograph and message.

848
01:03:01,397 --> 01:03:05,397
この後1時15分にカートオープンするよ！もうすぐだよね。
The cart opens after this at 1:15 PM! That's really soon.

849
01:03:05,397 --> 01:03:08,397
続いてアルバムです。Next up, the album!
Next up is the album. Next up, the album!

850
01:03:08,397 --> 01:03:13,397
This time, it's being released in two formats: the CD and vinyl! Woohoo!

851
01:03:13,397 --> 01:03:19,397
Pre-orders will begin also at 1:15 PM JST at the Hololive Production Official Shop, like real soon.

852
01:03:19,397 --> 01:03:24,397
As for digital releases, that will happen on July 12th.

853
01:03:24,397 --> 01:03:28,397
今回はCDとレコードの2種類のリリースとなっておりまして、
This time, it will be released in two formats, CD and vinyl,

854
01:03:28,397 --> 01:03:34,397
この後1時15分よりホロライブオフィシャルショップにて予約が開始されます。
and pre-orders will begin after this at 1:15 PM JST at the Hololive Official Shop.

855
01:03:34,397 --> 01:03:37,397
デジタルリリースは7月12日です。
The digital release will be on July 12th.

856
01:03:37,397 --> 01:03:42,897
CDにはここでしか聴けない「Gravity」のリアレンジバージョンとステッカー2種類、
The CD comes with a re-arranged version of 'Gravity' that you can only hear here, and two types of stickers.

857
01:03:42,897 --> 01:03:49,397
レコードにはジャケットとアナザージャケットが印刷されたLPサイズ両面ポストカードが付いてきます。
The vinyl comes with a double-sided LP-sized postcard with the cover jacket and alternate jacket printed on it.

858
01:03:49,397 --> 01:03:53,397
ポストカードじゃないよ、ポスターカード。もっとデカいです。
It's not a postcard, it's a poster card. It's much bigger.

859
01:03:53,397 --> 01:03:59,397
さらに、こちらのポスターカードには、両面のどちらかに必ず直筆サインが入ります！
Furthermore, one of the sides of this poster card will definitely be autographed by hand!

860
01:03:59,397 --> 01:04:05,397
サインされる面はランダムでございます。裏面かもしれないし、表面かもしれません。
The signed side is random. It could be on the back, or the front.

861
01:04:05,397 --> 01:04:11,397
The CD will include an exclusive re-arranged version of Gravity and two types of stickers,

862
01:04:11,397 --> 01:04:16,397
while the vinyl comes with a double-sided LP-sized poster card.

863
01:04:16,397 --> 01:04:22,397
Yes, a pretty darn big poster card featuring both the main and alternate album covers.

864
01:04:22,397 --> 01:04:28,397
Plus, yes a big plus, one side of this poster card will definitely feature a hand-written autograph!

865
01:04:28,397 --> 01:04:34,897
The signed side will be random, so it could be on either the alternate jacket side or the main album cover.

866
01:04:34,897 --> 01:04:37,397
We'll see when you get it!

867
01:04:37,397 --> 01:04:45,397
And BE MY FLAME, which was performed in today's 3D Live, will also be digitally released at midnight today, so don't forget to check it out.

868
01:04:45,397 --> 01:04:52,397
そしてライブでお披露目した『BE MY FLAME』は、24時にデジタルリリースもあるので、忘れずにチェックしてね！
And 'BE MY FLAME', which was revealed in the live concert, will also be digitally released at midnight, so make sure to check it out!

869
01:04:52,397 --> 01:04:55,397
And there's more! That's right!

870
01:04:55,397 --> 01:04:58,897
My first solo live concert! Woohoo!

871
01:04:58,897 --> 01:05:00,397
The venue will be...

872
01:05:00,452 --> 01:05:04,952
Tokyo at SGC Hall Ariake, woo!

873
01:05:04,952 --> 01:05:08,252
And it will be held on a Tuesday on October 6th.

874
01:05:08,252 --> 01:05:13,752
I'm super, super, super excited for this, and I'm so glad I've got to finally announce it!

875
01:05:13,752 --> 01:05:17,752
So I hope you guys will be really excited for it as well, yay!

876
01:05:17,752 --> 01:05:20,752
あとね、えっとソロライブも決まりました！
Also, my solo concert has been decided!

877
01:05:20,752 --> 01:05:24,752
場所は東京、SGCホール有明でございます。
The venue is Tokyo, SGC Hall Ariake.

878
01:05:24,752 --> 01:05:29,252
えーっと、開催される日程は10月6日火曜日です。
And the date of the event is Tuesday, October 6th.

879
01:05:29,252 --> 01:05:32,252
すっごく楽しみにしてるし、
I'm really looking forward to it,

880
01:05:32,252 --> 01:05:36,752
もうとにかく、もうこんなライブがやれる機会自体が本当に、
and honestly, an opportunity to perform a concert like this...

881
01:05:36,752 --> 01:05:39,752
まさかできると思ってなくて、
I never thought it would actually be possible,

882
01:05:39,752 --> 01:05:43,252
とってもワクワクしてますし、これからも準備頑張ります！
so I'm super excited and will do my best preparing for it from now on!

883
01:05:43,252 --> 01:05:48,052
Please look forward to further details and information in the future!

884
01:05:48,052 --> 01:05:52,752
Last but not least, there will be a members-only part starting at 1:30 PM pretty soon,

885
01:05:52,752 --> 01:05:58,052
so please come check it out if you can and join the family.

886
01:05:58,052 --> 01:06:01,252
最後に、メンバー限定パートが1時半から始まるので、
Lastly, the members-only part starts at 1:30,

887
01:06:01,252 --> 01:06:04,452
よかったらメンバーに入って見に来てね！
so if you'd like, please join the membership and come watch!

888
01:06:04,452 --> 01:06:07,752
では、ありがとうございました！
Well then, thank you so much!

889
01:06:07,752 --> 01:06:12,252
Thank you very much! Bye for now! Until the members' part!

